Daimler Turkey to Invest $200 Million in 2-3 Years, Dunya Says

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-03-31T06:07:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/daimler-turkey-to-invest-200-million-in-2-3-years-dunya-says.html
Mercedes-Benz Turk AS, a unit of
 Daimler AG (DAI) , will invest $200 million in two to three years in
 Turkey ,  Dunya  reported, citing chairman Wolf-Dieter Kurz.  The investment will be for production of buses and trucks
and also for research and development, Kurz said, according to
the Istanbul-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net . 